{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"AnimationEvent.elapsedTime","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/elapsedTime","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Construtor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propriedades</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/animationName\"><code>animationName</code></a></li><li><em><code>elapsedTime</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/pseudoElement\"><code>pseudoElement</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herança:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>Esta é uma <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tecnologia experimental (en-US)</a></strong><br>Verifique a <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">tabela de compatibilidade entre Navegadores</a> cuidadosamente antes de usar essa funcionalidade em produção.</p></div><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sumário","title":"Sumário","isH3":false,"content":"<p>O&nbsp;<code><strong>AnimationEvent.elapsedTime</strong></code>&nbsp;é uma propriedade só de leitura com um ponto flutuante dando a quantidade de tempo que animação esteve rodando, em segundos, quando o evento termina,&nbsp;excluirá&nbsp;o tempo em que ela esteve em pausa. Para um evento&nbsp;<code>\"animationstart\"&nbsp;</code>, <code>elapsedTime</code>&nbsp;é&nbsp;<code>0.0</code> a não ser que tenha um valor negativo para&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/animation-delay\"><code>animation-delay</code></a>, nesse caso o evento irá terminar com <code>elapsedTime</code> contendo&nbsp;<code>(-1 * </code><em>delay</em><code>)</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"síntaxe","title":"Síntaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">time = <em>AnimationEvent</em>.elapsedTime</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-animations-1/#AnimationEvent-elapsedTime\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Animations Level 1<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'AnimationEvent.elapsedTime' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Rascunho atual</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/6\" title=\"Released on 2011-08-16.\">6.0</a> (6.0)</td>\n   <td>10.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>6.0 (6.0)</td>\n   <td>10.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>43.0</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sect1","title":"&nbsp;","isH3":false,"content":"","titleAsText":" "}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/CSS/Using_CSS_animations\">Usando animações CSS.</a></li>\n <li>Animation-related CSS properties and at-rules: <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/animation\"><code>animation</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/animation-delay\"><code>animation-delay</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/animation-direction\"><code>animation-direction</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/animation-duration\"><code>animation-duration</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/animation-fill-mode\"><code>animation-fill-mode</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/animation-iteration-count\"><code>animation-iteration-count</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/animation-name\"><code>animation-name</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/animation-play-state\"><code>animation-play-state</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/animation-timing-function\"><code>animation-timing-function</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/@keyframes\"><code>@keyframes</code></a>.</li>\n <li>The <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a> interface it belongs to.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sumário","id":"sumário"},{"text":"Síntaxe","id":"síntaxe"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"&nbsp;","id":"sect1"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"O AnimationEvent.elapsedTime é uma propriedade só de leitura com um ponto flutuante dando a quantidade de tempo que animação esteve rodando, em segundos, quando o evento termina, excluirá o tempo em que ela esteve em pausa. Para um evento \"animationstart\" , elapsedTime é 0.0 a não ser que tenha um valor negativo para animation-delay, nesse caso o evento irá terminar com elapsedTime contendo (-1 * delay).","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"AnimationEvent.elapsedTime","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"AnimationEvent.elapsedTime","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"AnimationEvent.elapsedTime","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"AnimationEvent.elapsedTime","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/animationevent/elapsedtime","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/animationevent/elapsedtime/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent","title":"AnimationEvent"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/elapsedTime","title":"AnimationEvent.elapsedTime"}],"pageTitle":"AnimationEvent.elapsedTime - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}